.. highlight:: shell

============
Installation
============


Installation with pip (recommended)
-----------------------------------

To install , run this command in your terminal:

.. code-block:: console

    $ pip install 

This is the preferred method to install seaborn-qqplot, as it will always install the most recent stable release.

If you don't have `pip`_ installed, this `Python installation guide`_ can guide
you through the process.

.. _pip: https://pip.pypa.io
.. _Python installation guide: http://docs.python-guide.org/en/latest/starting/installation/


From sources
------------

The sources for seaborn-qqplot can be downloaded from the `Github repo`_.

You can either clone the public repository:

.. code-block:: console

    $ git clone git://github.com/matplotlib/seaborn-qqplot

Then, you can install it with:

.. code-block:: console

    $ cd seaborn-qqplot
    $ python setup.py build
    $ python setup.py install


.. _Github repo: https://github.com/matplotlib/seaborn-qqplot
